<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Return Request</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background-color: #4F46E5; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
    <h1 style="margin: 0;">SwiftShip AI</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div style="background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; margin-top: 20px;">
    <h2 style="color: #111827; margin-top: 0;">Return Request Received</h2>
    
    <p>We've received your return request and will process it shortly.</p>
    
    <div style="background-color: white; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #4F46E5;">
      <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Return Number:</strong> {{returnNumber}}</p>
      <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Order Number:</strong> {{orderNumber}}</p>
      <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Reason:</strong> {{reason}}</p>
      <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Request Date:</strong> {{returnDate}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>Our team will review your return request and get back to you within 24-48 hours. You'll receive an email once your return has been approved.</p>
    
    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
      <a href="https://swiftship.ai/returns/{{returnNumber}}" style="background-color: #4F46E5; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block;">View Return Status</a>
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px;">
    <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply.</p>
    <p>&copy; 2024 SwiftShip AI. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
